# Group Webhook

You can use webhook subscriptions to receive notifications about particular events. After you've subscribed to a webhook topic, your app can execute code immediately after specific events occur in bots that have your app installed, instead of having to make API calls periodically to check their status.

(To use in to the webhook, please contact [Customer support](mailto:customer-supoort@cresclab.com))

#### Considerations

MAAC OpenAPI does not have the endpoint `/partner/maac/binding/webhook/`, please do not use this for testing, this is just a design example, for reference only

| Topics                                    | Event                     |
| ----------------------------------------- | ------------------------- |
| receipt                                   | receipt.receipt_validated |
| form                                      | form.surveycake_submitted |
| LINE notification message status updated  | pnp.status_updated        |
| LINE notification message profile updated | pnp.profile_updated       |
| Prize Points Added                        | prize.points_added        |

> #### **Request**

`POST https://your-api-domain.com/your/webhook/endpoint`

> #### **Headers**

| column                   | value                                                                                                                   |
| :----------------------- | :---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Content-Type             | application/json; charset=utf-8                                                                                         |
| CrescLab-Idempotency-Key | A unique string identifier generated by MAAC. Uses this identifier to recognize subsequent retries of the same request. |
| CrescLab-Signature       | To confirm that the request was sent from the MAAC Platform.                                                            |

> #### **Body**

| column    | type   | description        |
| :-------- | :----- | :----------------- |
| timestamp | String | event triggered at |
| topic     | String | event topic        |
| data      | Object | event payload      |

## Webhook [/partner/maac/webhook/]

### Receipt Validated [POST]

+ Request (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (object)
        + `timestamp` (string) - event triggered at
        + `topic` (string) - event topic
        + `data` (object) - event payload
            + `line_uid` (string) - The unique user ID of the contact in the LINE official account, 33 characters in length
            + `customer_id` (string, nullable) - User ID of the third-party system
            + `campaign_name` (string, nullable) - campaign name
            + `number` (string) - receipt number
            + `datetime` (string) - transaction date time
            + `upload_datetime` (string) - receipt uploaded date time
            + `random_number` (string) - receipt random number
            + `channel` (string) - purchase channel
            + `items` (array) - purchase details
                + (object)
                    + `description` (string) - product description
                    + `unit_price` (number) - product prize
                    + `quantity` (number) - purchase counts
                    + `amount` (number) - total amount

    + Headers

            CrescLab-Idempotency-Key: 191fecc0b2644d3f875ce84b1340b645
            CrescLab-Signature: 0ff864b8f3bf8353e9a8e0b62f17da3be16cb66adf653561da482be93c836df5

    + Body

            {
                "timestamp": "2021-11-29T15:43:26.582968+08:00",
                "topic": "receipt.receipt_validated",
                "data": {
                    "line_uid": "U58c280fca6ea81aa18330cee7269d36b",
                    "customer_id": null,
                    "campaign_name": "串接測試",
                    "number": "JA87857072",
                    "datetime": "2021-11-09T12:05:36+08:00",
                    "upload_datetime": "2021-11-29T07:43:26.540452+08:00",
                    "random_number": "5067",
                    "channel": "師傅萬隆捷運站店",
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "description": "檸檬肉桂堅果橘皮",
