### Prize Points Added [POST]

+ Request (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (object)
        + `timestamp` (string) - event triggered at
        + `topic` (string) - event topic
        + `data` (object) - event payload
            + `prize_name` (string) - Prize Name
            + `points_id` (string) - The unique identification ID of the prize message, which can be used to identify the same point addition request
            + `points_category` (string, nullable) - Reward Points Category, the default is null, if MAAC has a setting, it will have a value
            + `line_uid` (string) - The unique user ID of the contact in the LINE official account, 33 characters in length
            + `customer_id` (string) - User ID of the third-party system
            + `points_memo` (string) - Reward Points Reason
            + `points_count` (number) - Reward Points Amount
            + `points_expire_date` (string, nullable) - Reward Points Expiration Date (ISO 8601 Format), the default is null, if MAAC has a setting, it will have a value

