### Message First Open [POST]
Once the messages sent via OpenAPI with the `event_id`, the webhook events will be delivered. Otherwise, there won't be any webhook events.

+ Request (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (object)
        + `timestamp` (string) - event triggered at
        + `topic` (string) - event topic
        + `data` (object) - event payload
            + `message_type` (string) - The type of the message. The value of this field will be one of the below, broadcast/openapi.
            + `message_id` (number) - The identification of each message. When `message_type` is `openapi`, the value of this field will be `event_id`.
            + `line_uid` (string) - The unique user ID of the contact in the LINE official account, 33 characters in length
            + `customer_id` (string) - User ID of the third-party system

    + Headers

            CrescLab-Idempotency-Key: 191fecc0b2644d3f875ce84b1340b645
            CrescLab-Signature: 0ff864b8f3bf8353e9a8e0b62f17da3be16cb66adf653561da482be93c836df5

    + Body

            {
                "timestamp": "2022-08-31T17:17:13.064761+08:00",
                "topic": "message.first_open",
                "data": {
                    "message_type": "broadcast",
                    "message_id": 999,
                    "line_uid": "U7ee656c217619d09bb51cd0198df98fd",
                    "customer_id": "xxx"
                }
            }


+ Response 200 (text/plain)
    + Body

            OK
